# 🌐 FB AutoPost PRO: AI-Powered Group Poster (SaaS)

Welcome to the ultimate solution for automated Facebook Group marketing. This tool uses **Vision AI** (Groq & Gemini) to generate viral captions based on your images and posts them automatically to your selected Facebook groups using your native Chrome browser.

---

## 🚀 Getting Started for Clients

Follow these 4 simple steps to start your automated marketing campaign.

### 1. Access the Dashboard
Visit our official Web Dashboard to manage your account status and pricing:
👉 **[YOUR-GITHUB-PAGES-URL-HERE]**

*   Log in with your email to track your post usage.
*   Check your member status (Free Tier or Premium).

---

### 2. Prepare Your Environment
You need to have **Python** and **Google Chrome** installed on your computer.

1.  **Install Python**: Download and install the latest version from [python.org](https://www.python.org/downloads/) (Make sure to check "Add Python to PATH" during installation).
2.  **Download the Agent**: Download this repository as a ZIP file and extract it to a folder on your computer.

---

### 3. Install Requirements
Open your **Terminal** or **PowerShell**, navigate to the extracted folder, and run:

```bash
pip install selenium webdriver-manager requests Pillow pyperclip
```

---

### 4. Run the Agent & Sync
Once the requirements are installed, launch the application:

```bash
python main.py
```

#### ⚙️ Configuration in the App:
*   **Email**: Enter the same email you used on the website.
*   **Cloud API URL**: Paste the API link provided on the dashboard (or contact support).
*   **API Keys**: Enter your free [Groq](https://console.groq.com/) or [Gemini](https://aistudio.google.com/) keys.
*   **Photos**: Select the folder on your computer containing the images you want to post.
*   **Facebook Setup**: Ensure you are **already logged in to Facebook** in your normal Google Chrome browser.

---

## 💎 Features & Benefits
*   **Vision AI Integration**: High-end AI analyzes your photos and writes captions that actually convert.
*   **Duplicate Prevention**: Remembers what you've already posted to keep your feed fresh.
*   **Safe Posting**: Runs from your own local machine and IP address, making it 100% safe from Facebook's anti-bot detection.
*   **Randomized Delays**: Simulates human behavior between posts to protect your account.

---

## 💰 Subscription & Limits
*   **Free Tier**: Post up to **5 high-quality posts** for free.
*   **Premium Tier**: Unlock **unlimited posting**, priority AI generation, and lifetime support. 
*   *Payments are currently processed via our secure Bank Gateway (See dashboard for details).*

